videos.description: Kyler Murray scrambles out of the pocket and connects with CeeDee Lamb for a 37-yard score early in the first quarter vs. Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Murray finds Lamb wide open for 37-yard TD

videos.description: TCU's KaVontae Turpin speeds through Oklahoma's defense and returns a kickoff 99 yards for a touchdown to answer a Sooners score in the first quarter.
videos.headline: TCU's Turpin returns kick 99 yards to the house

videos.description: Trey Sermon plows over a TCU defender and finds the end zone from four yards out to give Oklahoma a lead over the Horned Frogs.
videos.headline: Sermon powers into end zone for Sooners

videos.description: Kyler Murray runs the option and pitches to Kennedy Brooks, who breaks a tackle and scores a 21-yard touchdown to extend Oklahoma's lead over TCU.
videos.headline: Murray pitches to Brooks, leads to 21-yard TD

videos.description: After scoring a touchdown on Oklahoma's previous possession, Kennedy Brooks runs for 43 yards, setting up a Sooners touchdown later in the drive.
videos.headline: Brooks rips off 43-yard gain for Sooners

videos.description: Kyler Murray finds a soft spot in the TCU defense and throws his second touchdown of the game, this time to Lee Morris from 9 yards out.
videos.headline: Murray's 2nd TD pass goes to Morris

videos.description: KaVontae Turpin catches a screen from TCU backup QB Michael Collins and sprints up the sideline for a 41-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Turpin races past Sooners' defense for 41-yard TD

videos.description: TCU backup quarterback Michael Collins takes a shot into the end zone and hits Jalen Reagor for a 33-yard touchdown to cut into Oklahoma's lead.
videos.headline: TCU backup QB slings 33-yard TD

videos.description: Trey Sermon makes a cut, breaks a tackle and strides into the end zone from 33 yards away to add another touchdown for the Oklahoma Sooners.
videos.headline: Sermon scores 2nd rushing TD vs. TCU

videos.description: Kyler Murray runs play action and throws off his back foot to Carson Meier for his fourth touchdown pass vs. TCU.
videos.headline: Murray throws short for 4th TD pass

videos.description: Kennedy Brooks rushes for 168 yards as Oklahoma runs for a 323 yards in a 52-27 win over TCU.
